review: She was explaining everything very clearly, and she examined my teeth thoroughly and said what could have been done.She is down to earth when she was explaining

I had spacing between my teeth and was not happy with my smile. So I consulted the doctor here at icare family dentistry. She said 
that it was possible to close the space with composite filling process, and it took two sittings to finish the whole work. Now thanks to the team of doctors and their work, my smile looks way better than before and I am able to smile with confidence.

Doctor was very professional, courteous, friendly and made me feel like a family. I had to undergo a Implant surgery and Dr. Kalaivani did a great job, I felt that I was in a good hands. She explained me very well about the problem I have and given the treatment with care. Thanks to Dr. Kalaivani.
I would say this is a great place to go take care of your smile.
reply_text: Your positive feedback motivates us. Thanks for your kind review.
